{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"写在火热的车间","authors":["陈满平"],"dates":[{"year":1977,"month":3,"day":20}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"写在火热的车间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京第三棉纺织厂  陈满平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红色标语牌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好呵，红色标语牌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎朝阳，披霞彩——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工业学大庆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五个大字有气派！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上班打从牌前过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春风阵阵荡胸怀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼前是条大庆路呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"布机连着钻井台！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“铁人”精神照人心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"创业凯歌唱起来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学“两论”，攻难关，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东思想是统帅。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大庆出油咱出布，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车间成了布的海！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王张江姚“四人帮”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阴谋篡党怀鬼胎。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一脚窜进工厂门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就想砍倒标语牌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红色标语喷烈火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光芒四射驱阴霾。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就在这条标语前呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们擦亮眼睛识狼豺！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今朝又看标语牌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"容光焕发更丰采。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风雨过后更鲜红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜迎工人大步来！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抓革命，促生产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东风送暖花竞开——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万匹织锦披红霞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"标语牌下春如海……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老工长"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人称誉的不老松呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工长美名四方传，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热辣辣，火腾腾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"攻关抢险一身胆！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昨天书记作动员，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只见他的拳头攥出了汗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华主席的报告似春雷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一字一句动心弦！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深揭狠批“四人帮”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大好形势在眼前；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命生产浪推浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心里要比蜜糖甜！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"搞革新，闹夜战，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只见他回回排头站，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甩开膀子爱大干，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怀里揣着火一团！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，汽笛声声急，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"机轮隆隆转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老工长多象“火车头”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带着一个“英雄班”！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁要夸他是老模范，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他就板起面孔瞪大眼："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老啥咧？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五十六十正当年……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"name":"四人帮","type":"人物"},{"name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}